  [$ 4x^3 - 2x + 3 $], [$|  underline(2x + 1)$],
  [$ underline(-(4x^3 + 2x^2)) $], [$| 2x^2 - x - 1/2$],
  [$ -2x^2 - 2x + 3 $], [],
  [$ underline(-(-2x^2 - x)) $], [],
  [$ -x + 3 $], [],
  [$ underline(-(-x - 1/2)) $], [],
  [$ 7/2 $], []
)
$

$q(x) = 2x^2 - x - 1/2$ — частное, $r(x) = 7/2$ — остаток от деления $f(x)$ на $g(x)$.

$ f(x) = g(x) * underbrace((2x^2 - x - 1/2), q(x)) + underbrace(7/2, r(x)). $



